    "synopsis": "After Garm, Ragnar Blackmane is sent far from Fenris to ancient Terra as one of the Wolfblade, the Space Wolves honour-guard sworn to House Belisarius of the Navis Nobilite. Guarding Lady Gabriela Belisarius should be a duty of oath and tradition; instead Ragnar lands in a succession crisis around the dying Paternoval Envoy, with Navigator houses scheming, assassins moving and Chaos pressure leaking through Imperial politics. The saga shifts from saga-fire to court-intrigue: a Fenrisian hunter learning how lethal civilization can be.",
